The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 Mann caught for speech

 Chandigarh, June 14: Police have arrested Simranjit Singh Mann, Shiromani Akali Dal-Mann president, from Sangrur for making pro-Khalistani speeches at the Golden temple on June 6, the 21st anniversary of Operation Bluestar, reports our correspondent.

 Mann was on his way to a meeting when he was arrested. He is now in a police station. 




